      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Doubling your dose of Ventolin is a very risky idea, and you should absolutely not do that without professional guidance. Overusing rescue inhalers like Ventolin is a sign that your baseline asthma is not being managed properly, not that you need a bigger puff. Instead of self-medicating with more of the same, you need a proper assessment to find the root cause of this sudden shortness of breath.",
