    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i hear you. i just dont want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, it's so expensive here in mumbai. i've noticed my chest feels a bit tight and heavy too, almost like someone is sitting on it, but it goes away if i sit down for a minute. could that just be the asthma getting worse or maybe just anxiety from being stressed lately? it doesn't feel like an emergency, just really annoying.",
